import re

text = globals_schema.get("original_query", "")

course = re.search(r'Course.*?EAG V2', text, re.IGNORECASE)
email = re.search(r'Email ID: (.*?)(\n|$)', text, re.IGNORECASE)
master_name = re.search(r'Master's name: (.*?)(\n|$)', text, re.IGNORECASE)
course_taking = re.search(r'Which course.*?EAG', text, re.IGNORECASE)
dob = re.search(r'Date of birth: (.*?)(\n|$)', text, re.IGNORECASE)
marital_status = re.search(r'Marital status: (.*?)(\n|$)', text, re.IGNORECASE)


form_data = {
    "Course": course.group(0).split(':')[-1].strip() if course else None,
    "Email ID": email.group(1).strip() if email else None,
    "Master's name": master_name.group(1).strip() if master_name else None,
    "Which course is he/she taking?": course_taking.group(0).split(':')[-1].strip() if course_taking else None,
    "Date of birth": dob.group(1).strip() if dob else None,
    "Marital status": marital_status.group(1).strip() if marital_status else None
}

return {"form_data_0A": form_data}
